properties.name: Riverside
properties.description: Some flat spaces, many not flat spaces. Rocks and boulders.

properties.name: The Outpost
properties.description: Big barn, brewery, close to roads.
properties.comments: Make sure you know what you are doing if you are placing yourself here!

properties.name: The Grove
properties.description: A hilly forest with a burnt down Mansion, and two houses that has fallen over.
properties.comments: You need to have been here to place yourself here, please.

properties.name: The Outskirts
properties.description: Big meadow, tall grass, no service here. Not power, no toilets, no nothing.
properties.comments: You are on your own here. Radical Self Reliency! You have been warned.

properties.name: The Villa
properties.description: Some flat space, but lots of not flat space too.

properties.name: The Cold Wind Blows At Night
properties.description: Might not be cut and available, we dont know yet.
properties.comments: Low prio area, you should go north instead.

properties.name: The Village
properties.description: Nice natural feel, a grassy meadow.
properties.comments: Lots of high grass! Not easy-peasy.

properties.name: The Inner Garden
properties.description: Trees, rocks and a shed. Nice shade.
properties.comments: Be sure you know what you are doing if you are placing yourself here.

properties.name: The Sandpit
properties.comments: Not much flat space. Rocks and small trees.

properties.description: No camping here, the ground can not support it.
This field is not used this year, the ground can not support it.
